title: Vox Machina Ep. 65 - The Streets of Ank'harel
description: Vox Machina make their way to the distant continent of Marquet, traveling into the exotic city of Ank'Harel to seek allies and another vestige of power to aid in their war against the Chroma Conclave...and get slightly distracted.
